name: iridescent souls
description:
finally took some time to work on my own creative projects today and i love the way this piece came together. 'iridescent souls' image was created using NightCafe Studio's AI. The visual synthesis was created using Lumen. 

the green in the beginnign almost looks heavenly and it slowly shifts to red, where the darker colors reveal some hidden gems in the pieces. peep the eyes in the top of the frame, and some of the textures that get accented behind the souls themselves.
